        "text": "你不該站在岔路口， 剪除他們中間逃脫的人； 他們遭難的日子， 你不該把他們生還的人交出來。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "你不當站在岔路口剪除他們中間逃脫的； 他們遭難的日子， 你不當將他們剩下的人交付仇敵。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Do not stand at the fork of the road To cut down their fugitives; And do not imprison their survivors In the day of their distress."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "You should not wait at the crossroads to cut down their fugitives, nor hand over their survivors in the day of their trouble."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "You should not have stood at the crossroads, killing those who tried to escape. You should not have captured the survivors and handed them over in their terrible time of trouble."
      }
    },
